race.comment: MOEGREEN (2) grows a leg for rider Cormack who has four wins and three placings from just eight steers and has hit a purple patch of form recently. Is yet to miss a drum in five attempts over this seven-furlong journey and should be right there when the whips are cracking. BRAVE AGENDA (4) has finished runner-up in three of her past four starts and looks to be knocking on the door of another victory. Can make her presence felt. BURRANEER BUOY (5) has won two of his past three including getting the chocolates here at the latest effort. In the mix on best form. PRINCE AKEEM (9) has a strong second-up record with two wins and a second from four starts. Cannot be discounted lightly.
